Welcome back to What I=E2=80=99m Hearing, and Happy Valentine=E2=80=99s Day=
=2E
Hopefully everyone in Hollywood will take a break tomorrow from walking bac=
k D.E.I. commitments to spend time with loved ones.

Tonight it=E2=80=99s my chat with Netflix chief content officer Bela Bajari=
a. We kinda got into it over the movie strategy, quality vs. scale, Emilia =
P=C3=A9rez, what she=E2=80=99s buying, and misconceptions about the service=
 that ate Hollywood. Plus: some fun details from
inside the big SNL50 anniversary special, which is basically my Super Bowl.=
 (For the record, my viewership prediction for Sunday: 22 million live-plus=
-same-day viewers on NBC, E!, and Peacock.)

