That=E2=80=99s not what that
means. Our job is to make sure we know the creators out there doing really =
cool, interesting things, and what makes sense for Netflix. Some of them ma=
y be on YouTube, some of them may be in film school right now, some of them=
 may be at a festival that we=E2=80=99re gonna find.

But are you looking to do a big deal with a podcaster or YouTuber?

Anytime
we have a meeting or a conversation, it=E2=80=99s written about like we=E2=
=80=99re changing our strategy. So that=E2=80=99s very overstated.

But you did go after the MrBeast game show. Amazon ultimately, in my opinio=
n, overpaid for it.

You said it, I didn=E2=80=99t. (Laughs.) We did [bid for it]! Look, MrBeast=
 is a great talent on YouTube and was making a
big unscripted show very much like Squid Game. But he, you know, that was t=
he show that he made. We met with him, as did lots of other people.

The Greta
